we can still
get through this thing

15:47.067 --> 15:48.267
with a little bit
of dignity.

15:48.267 --> 15:50.434
You want me
to throw a fit on the floor

15:50.434 --> 15:53.367
like I do
when we can't pay at Denny's?

15:53.367 --> 15:55.100
That was for $3.95.

15:55.100 --> 15:57.267
For $225, they let you
swallow your tongue

15:57.267 --> 15:58.734
before they call an ambulance.

15:58.734 --> 16:00.601
Kelly,

16:00.601 --> 16:01.968
take the car keys,

16:01.968 --> 16:03.567
look at what
Mommy married,

16:03.567 --> 16:04.701
and bring back our money.

16:04.701 --> 16:05.801
Oh, oh, and,
Kelly--

16:05.801 --> 16:07.334
I know, I'll be careful.

16:07.334 --> 16:08.734
No, no,
I don't care about that.

16:08.734 --> 16:10.434
Just don't change
my radio station.

16:14.801 --> 16:16.801
Would you like me to take
your check now, sir?

16:16.801 --> 16:18.334
Uh, not quite yet.

16:18.334 --> 16:19.934
No, we'll just let
our meal settle here.

16:19.934 --> 16:21.400
We'll have some
more water, please.

16:21.400 --> 16:22.601
Can't get enough
water, you know.

16:22.601 --> 16:24.834
It's nature's
fruit juice.

16:27.167 --> 16:29.167
How long do you thing
it will take the kids?

16:29.167 --> 16:30.367
Well, it took us
40 minutes

16:30.367 --> 16:31.400
to get here one way,

16:31.400 --> 16:32.400
and knowing
how Kelly drives,

16:32.400 --> 16:33.601
they should be
here and back

16:33.601 --> 16:36.400
in about
eight minutes.

16:36.400 --> 16:38.434
Well, what are we gonna
do in the meantime?

16:38.434 --> 16:40.300
Just drink water.

16:42.434 --> 16:43.434
Got it, Kel?

16:43.434 --> 16:44.300
Got it.

16:50.234 --> 16:51.701
Confused again, Kel?

16:51.701 --> 16:53.734
Let me help.

16:53.734 --> 16:56.267
Turn the knob,
then open the door.

16:57.667 --> 17:00.934
No, young weenie.

17:00.934 --> 17:02.434
You know what just dawned on me?

17:02.434 --> 17:05.032
Two plus two equals four?

17:05.032 --> 17:06.501
Hey, when I'm not in school,

17:06.501 --> 17:09.367
I don't want to think about it,
okay?

17:09.367 --> 17:12.000
No, I was just thinking.

17:12.000 --> 17:13.800
You know, Mom and Dad
already got

17:13.800 --> 17:15.200
a great meal out of this money.

17:15.200 --> 17:17.200
I mean, they not going
to enjoy it any more

17:17.200 --> 17:18.767
by paying for it.

17:18.767 --> 17:20.601
Now we can enjoy it too.

17:20.601 --> 17:22.200
It's not too late
for Tears and Vomit.

17:22.200 --> 17:24.767
Wait a minute.
What about Mom and Dad?

17:24.767 --> 17:26.367
Come on, Bud.

17:26.367 --> 17:29.701
Who's better at beating a check
than Mom and Dad?

17:29.701 --> 17:31.501
God, I mean,
you were 9 before you knew

17:31.501 --> 17:34.300
that a movie theater
had a front door.

17:34.300 --> 17:35.501
Come on,
don't worry about them.

17:35.501 --> 17:37.300
Let's go.

17:37.300 --> 17:38.501
You realize if we do this,

17:38.501 --> 17:40.300
we might not be able
to come home tonight.

17:40.300 --> 17:42.467
Won't be a first for me.

17:46.567 --> 17:47.567
[PLAYING "MOON RIVER"
ON GLASSES]

17:47.567 --> 17:48.767
* Moon river *

17:48.767 --> 17:51.534
* Wider than a mile *

17:51.534 --> 17:54.267
* I'm crossing you in style-- *

17:54.267 --> 17:56.934
Peg, Peg, it's been
two and a half hours.

17:56.934 --> 17:57.934
It's safe to say

17:57.934 --> 18:00.200
the kids have
left us here to die.

18:00.200 --> 18:02.300
I can't believe the kids
would do this to us.

18:02.300 --> 18:04.434
Yeah, like we wouldn't
do it to them.

18:04.434 --> 18:05.934
[CLEARS THROAT]

18:05.934 --> 18:08.167
Would you like
to pay the check now?

18:08.167 --> 18:09.467
I'm letting
my water settle.

18:09.467 --> 18:11.033
Go away.
Go away.

18:11.033 --> 18:13.267
[PLAYING TANGO MUSIC]

18:16.133 --> 18:17.567
I got an idea.

18:17.567 --> 18:19.968
You'll pardon me
if I doubt you.

18:19.968 --> 18:21.701
And you'll pardon me
if I kill you.

18:21.701 --> 18:23.200
Come on, just
follow my lead.

19:12.667 --> 19:15.834
He overflowed
the toilet.

19:18.701 --> 19:20.100
What are we
going to do, Al?

19:20.100 --> 19:21.501
"What are we
going to do, Al?"

19:21.501 --> 19:22.901
"What are we
going to do, Al?"

19:22.901 --> 19:24.300
Well, when you're
out of the bedroom,

19:24.300 --> 19:28.834
the answers don't come easy,
do they, Peg?

19:28.834 --> 19:29.834
I got an idea.

19:29.834 --> 19:32.501
Boy, the ideas
sure come quick to you

19:32.501 --> 19:34.100
out of the bedroom,
don't they?

19:34.100 --> 19:36.334
Watch me operate.

19:39.501 --> 19:40.901
Billy Bob Sammy Jim!

19:40.901 --> 19:43.501
Hey, you old son of a gun,
where you been all these days?

19:43.501 --> 19:45.133
How long has it been,
six, seven years?

19:45.133 --> 19:47.534
Well, this must be the wife.
Boy, how he's talked about you.

19:47.534 --> 19:49.734
Listen, this might be
a bad time to bring it up,

19:49.734 --> 19:51.334
but remember
that $225.57 you owe me?

19:51.334 --> 19:52.968
Well, I was going
to let it slide,

19:52.968 --> 19:54.167
but that ruins friendships,
doesn't it?

19:54.167 --> 19:55.701
Oh, Harold.

19:55.701 --> 19:57.834
Well, to tell the truth,
I'm a little low.

19:57.834 --> 19:58.868
Well, whatever you got.

19:58.868 --> 20:00.467
Just, you know,
5, 10 bucks, you know.

20:00.467 --> 20:02.267
Send me the rest.
Hey, what's money among friends?

20:02.267 --> 20:03.467
Well,
I can give you $20.

20:03.467 --> 20:04.501
Well,
that's just great.

20:04.501 --> 20:05.501
Hey, it's been
really good--

20:05.501 --> 20:06.534
Yeah, yeah, right.

20:06.534 --> 20:08.367
Hey, Joe Bob Jack,
you old toe-picker, you!

20:10.634 --> 20:12.667
How'd you do,
Al?

20:12.667 --> 20:15.501
Well,
I was up to $75,

20:15.501 --> 20:17.267
then I ran into
somebody who knew me,

20:17.267 --> 20:18.701
so he saw me
with the money,

20:18.701 --> 20:20.901
I had to pay him
the $50 I owed him.

20:20.901 --> 20:23.968
Sir, it's been
three hours,

20:23.968 --> 20:25.834
and we really need
this table.

20:25.834 --> 20:29.100
We've got some nice water
for you to take home.

20:29.100 --> 20:30.434
Pay us!

20:31.267 --> 20:32.334
Didn't I pay?

20:32.334 --> 20:33.701
It must've
slipped my mind.

20:33.701 --> 20:34.601
Didn't I pay you?

20:36.234 --> 20:37.400
Oh, well.

20:37.400 --> 20:40.033
Listen, could you
bring me a newspaper?

20:40.033 --> 20:42.033
I'll be right back
with the manager, sir.

20:44.300 --> 20:45.801
Is it okay
to panic now, Al?

20:45.801 --> 20:47.801
Yeah, now would be
a good time to panic, Peg.

20:47.801 --> 20:49.400
What do you think
they'll do to us?

20:49.400 --> 20:50.501
Well,
it's a high-class joint.

20:50.501 --> 20:52.133
They'll probably
beat the hell out of me

20:52.133 --> 20:53.334
and toss me in a dumpster,

20:53.334 --> 20:54.567
but, well, you,

20:54.567 --> 20:56.167
you'll probably just have
to do some dishes.

20:56.167 --> 20:58.601
Dishes?

20:58.601 --> 21:00.767
Me?

21:00.767 --> 21:02.267
No way.

21:02.267 --> 21:03.434
I'm taking
charge here.

21:03.434 --> 21:04.434
Give me your shoes.

21:04.434 --> 21:06.000
What are you
talking about, Peg?

21:06.000 --> 21:08.767
Give me
your shoes, now.

21:10.000 --> 21:11.434
Sir,
if you can't pay,

21:11.434 --> 21:12.834
perhaps you'd like
to discuss it with--

21:16.467 --> 21:17.334
What's that?

21:18.434 --> 21:20.033
This!
Ugh!

21:21.767 --> 21:24.467
Okay,
everybody back.

21:24.467 --> 21:26.400
Now,
we're busting out of here.

21:26.400 --> 21:27.601
I want to see hands,
people.

21:27.601 --> 21:30.200
Nobody try
to be a hero.

21:30.200 --> 21:33.200
Oh, my God.
She's got a shoe!

21:33.200 --> 21:35.901
Nobody comes close,
nobody gets sick.

21:40.901 --> 21:43.300
And I don't want to see anybody
try that again.

21:43.300 --> 21:44.901
Let's go, Al.

21:52.534 --> 21:54.634
Play some happy music.

21:54.634 --> 21:59.033
[PLAYING "TIE A YELLOW RIBBON
'ROUND THE OLD OAK TREE"]

21:59.033 --> 22:00.567
Let's go, Al.

22:00.567 --> 22:01.868
Wait a second, Peg.

22:04.501 --> 22:05.501
You know,

22:05.501 --> 22:07.100
I had a really nice
time tonight, honey.

22:07.100 --> 22:08.701
It was nice getting out
for a change.

22:08.701 --> 22:09.801
Uh-huh.

22:09.801 --> 22:11.801
Hey, you wanna make
a run for the fire escape?

22:11.801 --> 22:13.200
You betcha.

22:22.667 --> 22:25.868
And don't try
to follow us.

